{"tid":440786,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"15小時4宗騙案呃走逾$330萬 上市公司總裁都中招","createTime":"2017-10-19T05:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T05:55:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e9f58c1ea7313876e509d2e6613fc5864c70ee48","tid":440786,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T05:38:17.000Z","msg":"電騙停不了，連上市公司總裁亦中招！昨日下午5時至今早8時，已先後有4宗電騙案，損失金額逾330萬港元。當中最大金額的一宗，49歲姓柳受害者，為本港一上市公司總裁，他接獲「入境處」來電，對方指他與一宗刑事案有關，其後電話轉駁至自稱是上海市公安的男子，柳不虞有詐，按指示將190萬元人民幣存入對方內地銀行戶口。<br />\n<br />\n柳於昨晚10時許報案，懷疑受騙，案件交由中區警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。除了柳被騙財外，昨日下午至今早，還有3宗電騙及詐騙案，受害人分別損失37萬港元、40多萬港元及25萬元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n根據該上市公司的網站資料，柳為該公司執行董事，兼任公司總裁，亦是上海一間資產管理公司的董事長。柳先後取得國際金融碩士及經濟法學博士學位。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》曾就事件向柳查詢，但其公司枱頭電話未有人接聽，職員指其不在辦公室。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57350479&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57350479%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171019&d=lqIhu9U%2BCmjjKJE3AlZIxJnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=042ce274\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57350479%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171019&h=d839c8ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57350479&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171019</a>"},{"pid":"5e4be67688df5ade7c8eb617509db80c8835eb67","tid":440786,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"新時代中國特色大茶飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f6ac819be72055266bdc4787640eb79d1deb6e","tid":440786,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T05:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0075aac85b2d15114908b